COMPILE ~BodhiNPC/scripts/YFBod25d.baf~
COMPILE ~BodhiNPC/scripts/YFBod25d.baf~
EXTEND_BOTTOM ~baldur25.bcs~ ~BodhiNPC/scripts/YFmiba25.baf~

