COMPILE ~BodhiNPC/scripts/YFBodElf.baf~

//Bodhi SoA Cutscenes
COMPILE ~BodhiNPC/scripts/YFBoJoin.baf~
COMPILE ~BodhiNPC/scripts/YFBoTran.baf~

